{"tid":1536973,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"香港一日內發生三單離奇死亡案件！！！點解冇人關注！！！！","createTime":"2019-09-03T18:31:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T19:01:00.000Z","uid":299808,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"efbaa6f2bd5d3886eaa6b4bcf9cd952cb167e4e9","tid":1536973,"uid":299808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T18:31:45.000Z","msg":"831太子站有三人仲未知去咗邊，完全人間蒸發咁。<br />\n然後封站直至九月三號，太子站解封後，今日新聞就馬上報咗有三單離奇死亡案件<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">喺香港一日內發生三單離奇死亡案件</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\np牌仔用小學雞程度嘅資料整合方式簡單整理咗三單案<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：<br />\n<br />\n<strong>1/  沙田官立中學 中二學生 （暫時未知叫咩名）</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dVGrQvX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdVGrQvX.png&h=a5245e4f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">死亡原因：『不幸離世』</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong>2/  天星碼頭  40歲浮屍女子（暫時未知叫咩名）</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/v8dBtju.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fv8dBtju.png&h=10db3c02&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">死亡原因：墮海，至於點墮海，警方仲調查中</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>3/  西貢<strong>懷疑謀殺案</strong> 21歲女子喺龍尾村村屋內死亡（暫時未知叫咩名）</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/f5rWtkW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ff5rWtkW.png&h=a1e931ed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">死亡原因：警方懷疑<strong>死者父母串謀另外一男一女<span style=\"color: purple;\">用手、拖鞋、膠拍</span>謀殺自己個女，然後死者父親發現女兒暈倒後報案</strong></span></span> 現在涉案四人被涉嫌謀殺被扣留<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">同我推上熱門<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n向警方近來查案極快嘅效率追問佢地查成點，另外三名太子站失蹤人口調查完未<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />拎到資料未啊屌你</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n冇比佢地蒙混過關啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d43fcc006590422ca0cb02d2a393b6c7f3aa007a","tid":1536973,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T18:31:51.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n烏克蘭, 法國等其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮, 唔割但要小心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外可參考唔揸春袋揸輸精管方法: <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n [行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n <br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"74bfed8acd84f3205cda1d4c47ab909bfeda6f34","tid":1536973,"uid":97330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T18:32:04.000Z","msg":"借位一推<br />\n快閃既勇武係唔洗代價<br />\n而且少人就成事，大家諗下一個廢老咁慢手腳都可以清晒連儂牆<br />\n對家打埋啲陰陰濕濕既招，我地都可以陰陰濕濕快閃一啲有價值既地方<br />\n重點：非狗屋 快閃 十八區都有既時候 啲狗跑得去邊？<br